<br>
I really don't give a rat's ass what you think of me or NE, but I can assure you NE members are warned to not respond to OOC or say comments. They never would have been allowed to do what your people did by being on that island or hanging out at the portal up. I would not tolerate any of them badgering any other guild members in tells and they have been called on it before. They know better. <br>
<br>
You want to claim a respectful guild and play fair? You ruined it last night in my eyes. Even then you still say you want to &quot;get along better.&quot; Cry me a river. <br>
<br>
Grey Hawk acted completely out of line with the GM ruling and allowing us our shot. However, when we failed, we left the zone and you completely alone. Oh yeah, we failed. That does happen usually on your first attempt of a God and when you have had to put up with idiots like you guys last night. <br>
<br>
Want to get along? Try growing up. I would be ashamed of my officers and members had they acted like you people last night. <br>
